31 §2423-F. Cannabis manufacturing facilities; cannabis extraction
32 Sec. 12. 22 MRSA §2423-F, first ¶, as repealed and replaced by PL 2019, c. 331,
33 §17 and amended by PL 2021, c. 669, §5, is repealed and the following enacted in its place:
34 This section governs the manufacture of cannabis products and cannabis concentrate
