413 adopted by the department pursuant to subsection 10 governing cannabis extraction using
424 inherently hazardous substances. A person that is not a qualifying patient, registered
435 caregiver, registered dispensary or manufacturing facility may not engage in cannabis
446 extraction using inherently hazardous substances.
