14 facility that is also a qualifying patient, registered caregiver or registered dispensary may
15 possess the amount of cannabis allowed for that facility under this section in addition to the
16 amount of cannabis allowed for a qualifying patient, registered caregiver or registered
17 dispensary under this chapter, as long as the cannabis possessed as a manufacturing facility
18 under this section is distinguishable from the cannabis possessed as a qualifying patient,
19 registered caregiver or registered dispensary under this chapter.
