132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST SPECIAL SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 1840
S.P. 723 In Senate, April 30, 2025
An Act to Amend the Maine Medical Use of Cannabis Act
Reference to the Committee on Veterans and Legal Affairs suggested and ordered printed.
DAREK M. GRANT
Secretary of the Senate
Presented by Senator HICKMAN of Kennebec.
Cosponsored by Representative BOYER of Poland and
